  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per turn, when you deal Acid Damage to a creature holding a weapon with weapon seals, the weapon becomes brittle. <br />If you deal damage to that same creature holding the same weapon three times this combat, the weapon is permanently damaged suffering a -2 penalty to hit and damage. <br />A weapon that suffers this traits effects twice in any single combat is destroyed. <br />A creature with a weapon damaged by this weapon can repair it with the Mending Jutsu.</p>",
